What is Cloud Computing?
Cloud Computing means renting servers, storage, networking and services over the internet instead of buying physical hardware.

Real-Time Scenario:
Company starts with 10 employees.

Instead of purchasing:

Server = ₹2 Lakhs
Storage = ₹50,000
Networking = ₹30,000

They use AWS and pay only for usage.

